data.description: 4K credit towards interior paint or concessions. 20K in upgrades in this beautiful newer Pahlisch home, open great room w/gas fireplace, beautiful kitchen w/quartz counter tops including an island w/eating area & ss appliances & lots of large windows for natural lighting & dining area leading to a covered back patio w/new hot tub & landscaped back yard. Large upstairs loft living area makes a great family gathering spot or home office, a roomy primary suite w/walk-in-closet & private bathroom & two guest bedrooms w/views of Barnes Butte, full guest bath & laundry room w/folding table near the bedrooms. Home features a gas furnace & fireplace to stay cozy in the winter & central air for those warm summer days. Neighborhood amenities include seasonal swimming pool, parks, play area, sports court, Ochoco Pointe community walking path to protected wetland reserve w/direct access to public & BLM trails up around Barnes Butte. HOA includes front yard maintenance.
